		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Blightthorn Vines",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>a Blightthorn Abomination has six vines, that it can use to grab a creature. A Creature can attempt to destroy the vines, by Strking at them. If the Blightthorn Abomination is grappling someone, the vines occupy both the Blightthorn Abomination's space and the grappled creature's space. the Blightthorn Vines have an AC of 17, 32 HP and has weakness 6 to both fire and slashing damage, while having the same immunity of the Blightthorn Abomination in addiction to immunity to mental damage). Destroying a Blightthorn vines also deals 10 damage to the Blightthorn Abomination. A creature can also destroy a Vine with a @Check[athletics|dc:25] checks</p>",
